n Chương ở thủy trại, liệu Thanh Long Yển Nguyệt Đao sẽ về tay ai đây?</p>","tmdb":{"type":"movie","id":"795793","season":null,"vote_average":6.5,"vote_count":6},"modified":"2023-03-15T16:18:37.000Z","cast":["Quan Trí Bân","Lu Shuming","Jin Song","Liu Weizhou","Naomen Eerdeni","Ma Ruihan","Dong Yanlin","Zhou Hang","Yuan Guogang"],"director":["Dai Yi Lin","Chen Si Ming"],"cast_meta":[{"name":"Quan Trí Bân","name_vi":"Quan Trí Bân","name_original":"Kenny Kwan","tmdb_id":130606,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/pKTpNYdL37MBwESmvAnVrHjBMc6.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/130606"},{"name":"Lu Shuming","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Lu Shuming","tmdb_id":1843208,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/wL2j1gUaezHsx1P9VRBxXBYc2X6.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/1843208"},{"name":"Jin Song","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Jin Song","tmdb_id":113792,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/fHAL9lT0HTeON5eOoDIcngoCyZC.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/113792"},{"name":"Liu Weizhou","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Liu Weizhou","tmdb_id":3247037,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/fISCOU6LzdrMM8volYJrM5iX4FY.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/3247037"},{"name":"Naomen Eerdeni","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Naomen Eerdeni","tmdb_id":2211206,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/zWoUp9KpTW2l2LLXRV4EE49PQEM.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/2211206"},{"name":"Ma Ruihan","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Ma Ruihan","tmdb_id":2974290,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/dq2nVSoGUHcDoCl04BkszbeWJnK.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/2974290"},{"name":"Dong Yanlin","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Dong Yanlin","tmdb_id":4766816,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/Vv8jGdZlSEnXshPkZ5GfLTNs9Z.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/4766816"},{"name":"Zhou Hang","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Zhou Hang","tmdb_id":2705522,"profile":null,